Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊 時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你可別遲到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關的這個你別碰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也別放進冰箱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 你很囉嗦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1簽 不平衡邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一般垃圾）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 麥男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊 快樂好運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著你在四月份會有最佳的運勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並可期待美好的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是別太期待的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺清心寡慾的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠參加今天的入學典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示你至少有過一次好運不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指抽中入學的簽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 搞不好我的好運全都用在那上頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請確認您的車票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信者得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點安慰效果都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜各位入學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立橋院高中已創校130年 擁有5000名學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其歷史與規模皆相當輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位新生能好好發揮各自的過人體力、智力與意志力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也期待各位的好運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭卡士達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部出席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該也沒人會在入學典禮就請假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一下子學生會應該會開始廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前可以自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用一一自我介紹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個你們自己做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的年紀已經不需要聽人發號施令了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師竟然一點幹勁都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分班之後才發現抽到爛簽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是好簽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師他不看名冊就喊出了大家的名字 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能大家很想認為自己運氣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得與自己無關似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能入學我就很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不奢望更多的好運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個「快樂好運」在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那樣叫我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查個資料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蕈類）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想拜託她別再買些莫名其妙的東西回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟那些是在哪裏？跟誰？又是花了多少錢買的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算姊姊那個德性 應該不至於是自己去採的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心的咖啡色 又皺巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂端帶著紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形狀為球形或不規則形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細部軟而白 多為圓柱狀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多生長於春天的針葉林帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度為5~8公分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極稀罕能長超過15公分 這就是鹿花菌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢字寫成「赤熊編笠茸」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶有劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要以水煮過 並避免吸入含有毒性的蒸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同青年的氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同臉頰紅潤的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種風味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同暢遊神僊世界般玄妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曉得蕈類就是菌類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孢子羞怯地長成菌絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菌絲合體後成為原基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原基成長後就是菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純而有力的生長過程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何遲疑與躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以孢子不斷繁衍的高等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是蕈類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了這種感覺喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 蕈類就會成為你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為你的導師 你的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時常相伴左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位應該都已經曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來將進行抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家各抽一張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面顯示的數字與文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表在這接下來的一年裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須奪取的職位 以及你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(508 會長 游泳池）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(006 會議 音樂教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(027 書記 烹飪教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我只認識你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當作會有新的邂逅就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又說這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽好簽後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請火速前往簽上記載的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 快樂好運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請勿吵鬧 迅速行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發現值得期待的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的一年真教人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烹飪教室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各團體成員確認完畢後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將舉行練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級生請擔任各場比賽的評審
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（烹飪教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是這裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（世界的蕈類）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也抽中烹飪教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 說不定只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發生好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？時乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朝霧小牧 擔任會計
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是秋山時乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我好像是學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘泉 我是副會長 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是榎本千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任書記 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到第一戰就跟你對上了 秋山時乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就怨嘆自己不走運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…同伴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是上石神井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上石神井蓮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們讀橡實山幼稚園白兔班 去遠足的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你拉走老師 慢吞吞地跑去上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我做什麼都是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是背誦地址 用漢字寫名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連加法也是我上石神井蓮子第一個學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你進了廁所 一直拖拖拉拉的不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是小蓮子啊 尿褲子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上石神井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過 不准叫我「同學」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我蓮子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸部很噁心耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 蓮子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將你送入地獄的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你們快點進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的比賽為熱身賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績將不列入記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間為60分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤數無上限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的規定就是必須使用指定的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸贏由會長判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食材就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏頭混有帶毒的種類 所以必須謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的關鍵就在於如何選擇蕈類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網柄牛肝菌 風味A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬菇 風味同樣為A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用電腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「用蕈類烹煮料理」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規定只有這一項
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 你看著好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊有時乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個含有α鵝膏蕈素與β鵝膏蕈素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一株就能讓一名成人致死的鱗柄白鵝膏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別名「死亡天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲膜菌 通稱「黑大國」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是蕈類專家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是喜歡蕈類罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點走火入魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有得忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要像她那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然一點用也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要我吃的話 我還蠻擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為討厭吃蕈類 會很討厭吃它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上沒人想知道你的飲食偏好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我就此倒下 不就正中秋山時乃的下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做出能拉大差距的料理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木、健司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在\N在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要學會世上最高境界的這本三顆星的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 蓮子小姐很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將切成兩半的螯蝦準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等平底鍋內的奶油熔化後 將螯蝦放上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮到半熟時從鍋內取出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後將鉚釘菇放入鍋內 吸取螯蝦及奶油的風味…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成她可以過目不忘？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 她很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他兩人只是聽從指示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就能做得那麼流暢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有命令就無法動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這就是填鴨教育的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮子小姐更厲害的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮子小姐\N蓮子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓鉚釘菇吸取風味後\N讓鉚釘菇吸取風味後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何處理螯蝦？\N該如何處理螯蝦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螯蝦是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她只記得住3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是驚奇的3分鐘默背術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很懂 不過真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會對人家感到佩服或望著人家出神嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你幫我拿個盤子對你來說太困難了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈類用水沖洗會讓美味流失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是要稍微泡一下 還是用濕布擦拭就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼烹煮這些蕈類？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出點子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡量保持原味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人品嚐到不同的風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒烤、燉湯、或是跟飯一起煮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是法國料理的大廚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很清楚自己並不具備那樣的廚藝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以倒不如製作簡單的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場練習賽頗出人意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你安排好的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為主題是蕈類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我早就知道她對蕈類特別瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我為什麼要故意這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 我也不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為了賴在你家不走的那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 你應該也明白抽籤是很神聖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的簽運的確都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的 你幹嘛喂時乃吃香菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害她發動了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時乃太貪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為這種時候沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出馬腳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你們桌上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的 什麼都沒有 空蕩蕩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山時乃 你也不過是這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的團隊如同踩到自己丟的香蕉皮滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又遇到午後雷陣雨 沒能準時赴約
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此搞砸了重要的商談與人際關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只有這種程度 也暗示著你們未來之灰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有5分鐘 你做得出什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算來洗鍋子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈類也只剩有毒的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿花菌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含有單甲基胺毒素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人出現嘔肚腹瀉等癥狀後致死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只要藉由煮沸將有毒成分完全去除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何蕈類比它還美味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在歐洲還被視為告知春天到來的蕈類 相當珍貴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 我就讓你們連半道菜都做不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木、健司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在\N在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得來表現一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由馬鈴薯做成的Knoedel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將SteinPilz與Pfifferlinge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}SteinPilz：德文「牛肝菌」；Pfifferlinge：德文「雞油蕈」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切碎了加在裏頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knoedel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德文的丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曉得會長是日德混血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意拍馬屁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山時乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保證這道料理的安全嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白這種蕈可以食用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們能保證已完全除去毒素了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是學生會長發生萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是會長的職責所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 既然你都吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來宣佈成績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈秋山時乃隊獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的可是三顆星食譜加上綜合日西中式口味的大餐耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還會輸給那麼寒酸的一小盤菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意你的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於食材的鮮度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算花了再多技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是比不上食材原本具備的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點不在於煮出法國或是中華料理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要做出蕈類料理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山隊將新鮮食材的力量發揮得淋漓盡致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他們獲勝的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底慘敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小律對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 榎本千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候回來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼久了？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為你還待在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不通知我一聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我判斷沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不再是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意娶我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.78,0:24:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來有什麼精彩表現？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們 而是秋山同學他們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠揍！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.48,0:24:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會認為秋山時乃才是「不簽」的女主角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.45,0:24:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說的話 我認為會長才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠揍…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.22,0:24:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角居然是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:24:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不過是長得漂亮了點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.59,0:25:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身是謎 胸部頗大 似乎有什麼過去之類的點點點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不平衡抽籤 下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.86,0:25:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狂風巨浪！立橋院高中學生會執行部」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師們也會登場
